[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":238},["Reactive",2],{"content-query-6vAmWQLT8p":3,"equal":33},{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":7,"description":5,"body":8,"_type":28,"_id":29,"_source":30,"_file":31,"_extension":32},"/credit","",false,"Credit",{"type":9,"children":10,"toc":25},"root",[11,16,21],{"type":12,"tag":13,"props":14,"children":15},"element","view-credit",{},[],{"type":12,"tag":17,"props":18,"children":20},"text-space",{"info":19},"* 由于本人并非专业人员，也未从事与安全研究员、渗透测试工程师或提供某种安全服务相关的工作，所以安全仅仅是我的个人兴趣。因此。在 'CREDIT' 卡片中发现的绝大部分漏洞都是歪打正着碰巧发现的。专业安全领域从业者、红队 / 蓝队等专业人士，以及硬件（HW）、CTF 等领域的工作者是我难以想象的高度，因此我无法媲美。在本网站有关安全的文章、CREDIT 以及本网站可能存在较大的书写问题，甚至在某些专业和领域的书面表达上可能质量较低，请谅解。\n\u003Cbr /> \u003Cbr />\n我深知在任何与技术相关的领域中，关注应用、效果以及解决问题是最重要的。任何过于花哨的设计或过多的描述都只是为了掩盖问题的本质。在技术领域中有一句流传的佳话：' 技术领域，菜是原罪 '。因此，我对安全领域的工作者们的工作充满向往。我一直认为编写安全报告是一件很酷的事情，尤其是在处理涉密信息时，这种感觉变得更加强烈（因为涉密信息是普通人难以接触的）。每当我有空闲时间，我都会浏览 Hack the Box Academy，体验专业的安全从业者所需要的课程或工作场景（这让我觉得安全从业者都很酷很帅）。\n\u003Cbr /> \u003Cbr />\n特别是在各种工具的开发中，在通过终端运行时我总能感受到技术上的纯粹美感。无论是交互式环境还是 GUI，与安全领域相关的一切都特别吸引我，它们的设计和代码简直是巧夺天工，是我此生渴望达到的目标。\n\u003Cbr /> \u003Cbr />\n我在 CREDIT 中筛选了我自 2019 年至今所提交且可以公开的漏洞。由于这些漏洞都是我在学生时代或年幼时无知而懵懂操作的结果，因此它们并不具备深度的技术描述或针对特定知识点的说明。如果您是技术或安全领域的从业者，或对相关行业有兴趣的人，很抱歉浪费了您 1~2 分钟的时间，对此我深感抱歉和愧疚。 ",[],{"type":12,"tag":22,"props":23,"children":24},"page-tips",{},[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":27},2,[],"markdown","content:credit.md","content","credit.md","md",[34,203,221],{"_path":35,"_dir":36,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":37,"description":38,"platform":39,"director":40,"types":41,"vulnerability":42,"release_date":43,"demo":44,"images":45,"body":46,"_type":28,"_id":201,"_source":30,"_file":202,"_extension":32},"/credit/github-misconfiguration","credit","GraphQL Misconfiguration in CWE-16 Github API","这是我第一次提交漏洞获得赏金和周边奖励的漏洞，所以我印象深刻。自我放弃安全路线以来，再一次发现较为知名厂商或平台的安全缺陷，可以当做是我的里程碑，但并不是终点。","/images/credit/logo/hackerone.png","RHYME.Q","CREDIT","CWE-16","2023.12.04","https://hackerone.com/iepn","/images/credit/github.png",{"type":9,"children":47,"toc":199},[48,54,60,94,123,127,132,137,142,147,152,157,162,167,172,177,182,196],{"type":12,"tag":49,"props":50,"children":53},"page-img",{"img":51,"title":52,"url":44},"cwe-github/home","CWE-16 Github API",[],{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":56,"children":57},"p",{},[58],{"type":59,"value":38},"text",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":61,"children":62},{},[63,65,74,76,83,85,92],{"type":59,"value":64},"我很喜欢 Github 的章鱼猫，我也遇到过身边有好友将章鱼猫当做自己的头像来使用。封面上的章鱼猫来自 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":67,"children":71},"a",{"href":68,"rel":69},"https://octodex.github.com/",[70],"nofollow",[72],{"type":59,"value":73},"GitHub Octocats",{"type":59,"value":75}," 他的设计师是 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":77,"children":80},{"href":78,"rel":79},"https://jeejkang.com/Information",[70],[81],{"type":59,"value":82},"@James Kang",{"type":59,"value":84},"，您可以在 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":86,"children":89},{"href":87,"rel":88},"https://myoctocat.com/",[70],[90],{"type":59,"value":91},"myOctocat",{"type":59,"value":93}," 中创建属于自己的章鱼猫。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":95,"children":96},{},[97,99,106,108,113,114,121],{"type":59,"value":98},"在 2011 年中，GitHub 决定是时候升级他们的吉祥物 Octocat 了,所以 Github 邀请了很多设计师对章鱼猫进行创作，如 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":100,"children":103},{"href":101,"rel":102},"https://cameronmcefee.com/work/the-octocat/",[70],[104],{"type":59,"value":105},"Cameron McEfee",{"type":59,"value":107},"、",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":109,"children":111},{"href":78,"rel":110},[70],[112],{"type":59,"value":82},{"type":59,"value":107},{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":115,"children":118},{"href":116,"rel":117},"https://www.kimestoesta.com/",[70],[119],{"type":59,"value":120},"@KimEstoesta",{"type":59,"value":122}," …… 等",{"type":12,"tag":17,"props":124,"children":126},{"info":125},"从笔记本电脑上的贴花和衣服上的图形，到每个酒吧墙上、电线杆和街道标志上贴的贴纸，GitHub 的吉祥物 Octocat 是科技行业最知名的符号之一。@Cameron McEfee",[],{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":128,"children":129},{},[130],{"type":59,"value":131},"其中 James Kang 设计的章鱼猫之一的 Private Investocat 作为 Github Security - GitHub Bug Bounty 的标志性头像。",{"type":12,"tag":17,"props":133,"children":136},{"info":134,"img":135},"图 1 | 我很幸运在他们立项后的 13 年后，获得了它们的实体周边贴纸和胸针。他们的设计师是 @KimEstoesta 和 @Cameron McEfee","7/1",[],{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":138,"children":139},{},[140],{"type":59,"value":141},"同时我还收获到了来自 Github Bug Bounty 的 $200 USD ≈ 1,439 CNY 漏洞赏金，是我在安全道路中，第一次获得如此高昂的现金奖励。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":143,"children":144},{},[145],{"type":59,"value":146},"可惜我的定位一直就是团队中的 ACD（辅助）成长缓慢容易给单杀 0_0，一直处于打酱油的状态，有很多方面的技能树需要提升。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":148,"children":149},{},[150],{"type":59,"value":151},"自意识到安全是基于开发之下的存在后，我便开始尝试慢慢往开发方面转型，曾经我的老师之前说过：“如果真的有天赋，那不应该将时间投入到应用和框架当中，应该聚焦原理和底层逻辑的设计”。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":153,"children":154},{},[155],{"type":59,"value":156},"很明显我属于任何天赋为 0，基础薄弱，一生中无法有较大的成就。在我认识到自身的差距以后，我开始变得不善于与人交谈，退出了所有社区群组，慢慢提升自己。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":158,"children":159},{},[160],{"type":59,"value":161},"但等我真正见识到那些在各项比赛中大放异彩的选手后，以及在各类排行榜轻松拿下 10W、30W 奖励赏金的安全专家后，我开始没了当年的自信。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":163,"children":164},{},[165],{"type":59,"value":166},"慢慢的我意识到，有时候也许并不需要很好看的界面、很优雅的 Code，很完美的逻辑处理甚至是低的安全性，只需要一个噱头而已，让他们知道你可以就行了，并不需要做的很完美。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":168,"children":169},{},[170],{"type":59,"value":171},"我身边有很多例子，在发展到一定程度后，就会产生一种 “工匠精神”，开始意识到之前做的并不好，因此追求更高的标准。",{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":173,"children":174},{},[175],{"type":59,"value":176},"因此我一生中最敬佩的只有两种人，一种是追求这种境界成功的或正在追求这种境界的。而另一种是没有追求这种境界的，一直停留在最开始阶段的人。",{"type":12,"tag":17,"props":178,"children":181},{"info":179,"img":180},"开源社区有那些热情且对技术拥有浓厚兴趣的追求者，也有一些沉默的大多数，虽然一次也没有提交过 PR，仓库里诠释 Fork 的热爱，在 Issue 挥洒文字与热情的人。以及在各类平台分享项目对 Code 逻辑评头论足的专业 Code 评审们，TA 们构成了开源社区。","7/2",[],{"type":12,"tag":55,"props":183,"children":184},{},[185,187,194],{"type":59,"value":186},"我的第一个 github pr 是在两年前，当时我还在学校。学习 Node.js 途中认识到了 ",{"type":12,"tag":66,"props":188,"children":191},{"href":189,"rel":190},"https://expressjs.com/",[70],[192],{"type":59,"value":193},"expressjs",{"type":59,"value":195},"。毫无疑问的说，我第一次感受到来自开源社区的热情，因此我非常喜欢开源社区的氛围。",{"type":12,"tag":22,"props":197,"children":198},{},[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":200},[],"content:credit:github-misconfiguration.md","credit/github-misconfiguration.md",{"_path":204,"_dir":36,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":205,"description":5,"platform":206,"director":40,"types":41,"vulnerability":207,"release_date":208,"demo":209,"images":210,"body":211,"_type":28,"_id":219,"_source":30,"_file":220,"_extension":32},"/credit/edraw","亿图图示水印导出逻辑漏洞","/images/credit/logo/cnvd.png","CWE-703 | CNVD-2021-24498","2021.05.01","https://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/3173261","/images/credit/edraw.png",{"type":9,"children":212,"toc":217},[213],{"type":12,"tag":49,"props":214,"children":216},{"title":215},"CNVD-2021-24498h",[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":218},[],"content:credit:edraw.md","credit/edraw.md",{"_path":222,"_dir":36,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":5,"title":223,"description":5,"platform":206,"director":40,"types":41,"vulnerability":224,"release_date":225,"demo":226,"images":227,"body":228,"_type":28,"_id":236,"_source":30,"_file":237,"_extension":32},"/credit/china-telecom","广东电信 IPTV 支付系统存在逻辑缺陷漏洞","CWE-703 | CNVD-2020-10601","2020.02.04","https://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/1976603","/images/credit/china-telecom.png",{"type":9,"children":229,"toc":234},[230],{"type":12,"tag":49,"props":231,"children":233},{"title":232},"CNVD-2020-10601",[],{"title":5,"searchDepth":26,"depth":26,"links":235},[],"content:credit:china-telecom.md","credit/china-telecom.md",1710731932307]